<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Baseball Stats</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Baseball Team Statistics</h1>

<table border="1">
    <caption>2025 Varsity Baseball Player Stats</caption>

    <tr>
        <th rowspan="2">Player Name</th>
        <th colspan="2">Batting Stats</th>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <th>Batting Average</th>
        <th>Home Runs</th>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <td>John Smith</td>
        <td>.320</td>
        <td>5</td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <td>Alex Johnson</td>
        <td>.285</td>
        <td>3</td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <td>Chris Lee</td>
        <td>.301</td>
        <td>4</td>
    </tr>

</table>

<h2>Team Strengths</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Strong batting averages across players</li>
    <li>Consistent home run hitters</li>
    <li>Good team coordination and defense</li>
</ul>

</body>
</html>
